# Summary
Amplitude Data is a centralized tracking plan solution that helps define, track, and validate product analytics, ensuring consistent event collection across teams and platforms while providing tools for developers to simplify analytics implementation with type-safe tracking libraries, code linting, and a unified API that works across common development platforms.

